==English==

===Etymology===
Old English [[hleapan|hlēapan]], from Germanic ''*xlaupan''.  Cognate with Dutch [[lopen]], German [[laufen]] ‘run’, Swedish [[löpa]].

===Pronunciation===
* {{AHD|lēp}}, {{IPA|/liːp/}}, {{SAMPA|/li:p/}}
